y = L\(P*b);
x_piv = U\y;
err_piv = norm(ones(n,1)-x_piv,inf)/norm(ones(n,1),inf)
```

Transform Ax=b into Rx=Q'b; keep only the top n-by-n block of R and the first n entries of c.
```matlab
[Q,R] = qr(A);
c = Q'*b;
Rt = R(1:n,1:n);   % R-tilde, non-singular
c1 = c(1:n);
cstar = Rt\c1      % least-squares solution
```

